Copy librgba.tar.gz to /usr/ports/distfiles
Install gtk2-murrine-engine and murrine-based themes

Add export GTK_MODULES=rgba to .profile
Set environment variable GTK_RGBA_APPS (add to .profile)
export GTK_RGBA_APPS= list of applications

Set it to colon-separated list of applications to activate rgba ONLY in these apps:
GTK_RGBA_APPS=gedit:app2:app3

Prepend "allbut" to start to activate rgba in ALL apps except listed:
GTK_RGBA_APPS=allbut:gedit:app2:app3
